title: QB Taylor out for Bills game against Jaguars in London
text:
> Florida QB Taylor out for Bills game against Jaguars in London Buffalo Bills head coach Rex Ryan, right, talks with team owner Terry Pegula during an NFL training session at the Grove Hotel in Chandler's Cross, England, Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015. The Buffalo Bills play the Jacksonville Jaguars at Wembley stadium in London on Sunday in a regular season NFL game. (AP Photo/Matt Dunham) Search Help
